snippet.description:
The reason why Park Ji-hoon, CEO of Incheon Brewery, made the Gaehangro beer was simple.
"I wanted people to be able  to drink beer that I made in my area."
It was because of the desire to make beer that local people like and beer that people come to drink. And at the base was the hope that his favorite hometown would be revitalized.
